==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dewretting
<hw>Dew"ret`ting</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Dewrotting; the process of
decomposing the gummy matter of flax and hemp and setting the fibrous
part, by exposure on a sward to dew, rain, and sunshine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dewrot</ent>⟦br⟧
